---
title: Beef Rump & Sunny Veggie Toss with Balsamic Glaze
description: Beef is always nice cooked with light flavours, but a dark and rich balsamic glaze really takes it up a notch. With delicious root veggies in a cosy and vibrant toss, this might be the new best way to eat beef.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b839657f7b48609c8b1849-1eae0b14.jpeg
